			<div>
				<div class="w-2/5">
					<div class="text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
						AI Guardrails - Secure Your AI Implementations
					</div>
					<p class="mb-6 leading-loose">
						A robust solution designed to ensure the safe and ethical use of AI.
						Helps prevent risks of harmful content, unauthorized AI
						manipulations, and prompt injections, while also safeguarding
